data.description: Amazing pool & spa situated on Mountain Falls Golf Course! Oversized lot w/104 feet of golf course frontage! Spa waterfalls to contemporary custom pool, cool decking surrounds, & mtn views can't be beat! Over 2k sqft home, floor-to-ceiling windows looking to golf course, & tile flooring throughout! Open kitchen w/island, pendant lights, stainless appliances, granite tops, & pantry. Primary suite has slider to patio, jetted tub w/chandelier, walk-in shower, dual sinks, walk-in closet w/custom built-ins, & separate. Open den, shutters, 3 bed, 3-car garage w/storage cabinets, & finished landscaping w/irrigation on timer. Living room has built-in entertainment center, upgraded LED lighting, & ceiling fans in 5 rooms. Extended pavers to pool/spa, gated pet area, & gutter system. Community has 18-hole golf, driving range, pro shop, restaurant, full fitness center/gym, 3 pools, 45min to Vegas, 1hr to international airport. Valley has 3 wineries, golf, gaming, & endless trails!
